729728f-a.text:
(1)
3rd Street, east side, between New Dorp Lane and Rose Ave. (New Dorp), showing the Chiesa della Trinita, an lItalian Moravian church. It is also known as Trinity Moravian (Italian) church.
August 2, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
(2)
The same, another view. The house on the right, adjoins the
church to the south and bears No. 130.
August 2, 1929.
P. L. Sperr.
